~ start_chicken_pasture_box
Pasture Box: [[Hi|Hello|Howdy]], your chickens look hungry.
Pasture Box: They’ve been scratching around waiting for their meal.
Pasture Box: Would you like to feed your chickens now?
- Yes
	Arlo: Yeah! Let's feed my chickens.
	Pasture Box: Perfect! Well-fed chickens lay better eggs.
	Pasture Box: I’ll spread the feed for them.
	Pasture Box: Check back later to make sure they stay healthy.
	do GameDialogueManager.action_feed_animals()
- No
	Arlo: No, I don’t want to feed them right now.
	Pasture Box: Alright. Just remember—hungry chickens lay fewer eggs.
	Pasture Box: Come back anytime if you change your mind.
